examples.en: David has been in Garden City for more than three months.
examples.cn: 戴维住在花园城市已有3个多月了。

examples.en: You'd better have a big breakfast in the morning so as not to be hungry before lunch.
examples.cn: 你最好上午吃一顿丰盛的早餐,这样午餐前就不会觉得饿了。

translations.translation: 最大的;最多的;大多数的;大部分的

examples.en: Peter made the most mistakes of all the class.
examples.cn: 全班同学中,彼得犯的错最多。

examples.en: It was the most exciting holiday I've ever had.
examples.cn: 那是我经历过的最令人兴奋的假日。

expand: mostly adv. 主要地;一般地;通常

examples.en: My mother is nearly 80 and she's starting to get a bit forgetful.
examples.cn: 我的母亲近80岁,她开始有点健忘。

examples.en: Gilbert went there by motorcycle.
examples.cn: 吉尔伯特骑摩托车去的那儿。

examples.en: On the Double Ninth Festival, people usually climb mountains.
examples.cn: 在重阳节,人们通常去爬山。

examples.en: The baby likes to watch Mickey Mouse cartoons best.
examples.cn: 宝宝最喜欢看米老鼠卡通片了。

examples.en: Don't speak with your mouth full.
examples.cn: 嘴里塞满东西时不要讲话。

examples.en: Before moving into the new house, Mr. Andy is thinking of buying pieces of furniture.
examples.cn: 在搬进新房子之前,安迪先生想买几件家具。

examples.en: Many historical movies will be shown on National Day.
examples.cn: 许多历史影片将在国庆节上映。

examples.en: He owes a lot of money to Mr Smith.
examples.cn: 他欠史密斯先生许多钱。

examples.en: Mrs Jones gave music lessons at a school.
examples.cn: 琼斯太太在一所学校教音乐。

translations.translation: (修饰不可数名词)许多的,大量的

examples.en: I know how much trouble you have suffered.
examples.cn: 我知道你遭受过多大的痛苦。

examples.en: My deskmate Tom's handwriting is much better than mine.
examples.cn: 我的同桌汤姆的字写得比我的好。

examples.en: You saw her, Mum?
examples.cn: 你看见她了吗,妈妈?

examples.en: This warning sign must be put outside the gate of the museum.
examples.cn: 这样的警示标志必须放在博物馆的门口。

examples.en: Do you like mushroom soup?
examples.cn: 你喜欢蘑菇汤吗?

examples.en: The music he was playing was so beautiful. We all lost ourselves in it.
examples.cn: 他演奏的音乐是如此优美。我们都陶醉了。

expand: musician n. 音乐家;作曲家

translations.translation: 必须;需要;应当;必定是;一定

examples.en: Must I get everything ready for the discussion before the weekend?
examples.cn: 为这次讨论,我必须在周末前准备好一切吗?

examples.en: My name is Alice. I'm a girl.
examples.cn: 我的名字叫爱丽丝,是一个女孩。

examples.en: Can you name the flower?
examples.cn: 你能叫出这花儿的名字吗?

examples.en: On his way home he came to a narrow bridge over a stream.
examples.cn: 在回家的路上,他来到一座横跨在小河上的窄桥。

examples.en: The nation's economy is growing rapidly.
examples.cn: 这个国家的经济在快速增长。

expand: national adj. 全国性的;国家的;民族的

translations.translation: 全国性的;国家的;民族的

examples.en: What day is your National Day?
examples.cn: 你们的国庆节是哪一天?

examples.en: What's your nationality, Chinese or Japanese?
examples.cn: 你是什么国籍,中国籍还是日本籍?

examples.en: At the end of every year some people go back to their native homes.
examples.cn: 每年年终,有些人要回故乡去。

examples.en: Are you a native, or just a visitor?
examples.cn: 你是本地人还是游客?

examples.en: Earthquake is one of the natural disasters on the earth.
examples.cn: 地震是地球上的自然灾害之一。

expand: naturally adv. 自然地;天然地

examples.en: Nature is the glass reflecting truth.
examples.cn: 自然是反映真实的镜子。

examples.en: The teacher kept the student in because he was naughty.
examples.cn: 那个学生因为顽皮,放学后被老师留在学校里。

examples.en: Don't play near the road.
examples.cn: 不要在马路附近玩。

expand: nearby adj. 附近的;邻近的
nearly adv. 将近;几乎;差不多

examples.en: He works in the nearby police station.
examples.cn: 他在附近的警察局工作。

examples.en: I watch a match nearly every weekend on TV.
examples.cn: 我几乎每个周末都看电视上的比赛。

examples.en: We all want people to like us, so it is necessary for us to do what we can to please others.
examples.cn: 我们都希望别人喜欢我们,所以我们必须做一些能使其他人开心的事情。

examples.en: You needn't wash your car at the moment. It's going to rain.
examples.cn: 你这会儿不用洗车。要下雨了。

examples.en: This old woman is my neighbour.
examples.cn: 这个老妇人是我的邻居。

expand: neighbourhood n. 邻近地区,街坊,街区

examples.en: We have learned to help our parents at home and people in our neighbourhood.
examples.cn: 我们学会了在家里帮助父母,在小区帮助居民。

examples.en: Peter's parents are good at physics, but neither of them is good at English.
examples.cn: 彼得的父母擅长物理,但他们的英语都不行。

examples.en: She doesn't like swimming and neither does her sister.
examples.cn: 她和姐姐都不喜欢游泳。

examples.en: He feels nervous when he faces so many people.
examples.cn: 面对那么多人,他感到紧张。

examples.en: The fishermen are mending their nets.
examples.cn: 渔民们正在补渔网。

examples.en: They have built the national network.
examples.cn: 他们建成了全国性的网络。

examples.en: He never plays football in the street, does he?
examples.cn: 他从不在街上踢足球,是吗?

examples.en: The girl is so clever that she can memorise all these new words quickly.
examples.cn: 这个女孩很聪明,她很快就能记住所有这些新单词。

translations.translation: 新闻;消息;媒体对重要事情的报道

examples.en: The students have already learned the good news, haven't they?
examples.cn: 学生们已经知道这个好消息了,不是吗?

examples.en: What a wonderful newspaper 21st Century is!
examples.cn: 《21世纪报》是一份多么好的报纸啊!

translations.translation: 最近的;紧挨着的;隔壁的;下一次的

examples.en: Basil told us that he would be careful with electricity next time.
examples.cn: 巴兹尔告诉我们,下次用电他会小心。

translations.translation: 令人愉快的;好的;漂亮的

examples.en: Hello, Anna! Nice to meet you.
examples.cn: 你好,安娜!很高兴认识你。

examples.en: It is harmful for the little child to watch too much TV every night.
examples.cn: 小孩每天晚上电视看得太多是有害的。

examples.en: Only you can do such a thing, I'm sure, and nobody else has such an ability.
examples.cn: 我敢肯定,只有你能做这样的事情,别人没有这样的能力。

examples.en: Please be quiet. We are not allowed to make much noise in the reading room.
examples.cn: 请安静。不允许在阅览室里发出噪音。

expand: noisy adj. 嘈杂的,喧闹的

examples.en: It's too noisy here.
examples.cn: 这里太吵了。

examples.en: I'm hungry. Is there any bread in the fridge? None, but we have cakes. Would you like to have one?
examples.cn: 我饿了。冰箱里有面包吗?没有,但有蛋糕。你想要一个吗?

examples.en: I think you can have noodles.
examples.cn: 我想你们可以点面条。

examples.en: She can't get there at four, nor can I.
examples.cn: 她4点到不了那儿,我也不能。

examples.en: Such fish is rarely met with in the north country.
examples.cn: 这种鱼在北方地区难得看到。

examples.en: My nose is yellow, too.
examples.cn: 我的鼻子也是黄色的。

translations.translation: 便条;笔记;钞票;记录;音符

examples.en: Please take the note to the teacher.
examples.cn: 请把这张便条交给老师。

examples.en: Students should learn to protect themselves. Nothing is more important than life.
examples.cn: 学生要学会保护自己。没有什么比生命更重要。

examples.en: We'd better put up a notice here.
examples.cn: 我们最好在这儿贴一张布告。

examples.en: Did you notice him leave the house?
examples.cn: 你注意到他离开那个房子了吗?

examples.en: She spent a peaceful afternoon by the river, reading a novel.
examples.cn: 她在河边看小说,度过了一个宁静的下午。

examples.en: Thanksgiving Day falls on the fourth Thursday in November in the U.S.A.
examples.cn: 美国的感恩节是在11月的第四个星期四。

examples.en: Now let's talk about what a main idea is and how to find out the main idea.
examples.cn: 现在让我们来谈谈什么是主要思想,及如何找出主要思想。

examples.en: Nowadays vlogs are much more useful than traditional diaries and especially welcomed by young people.
examples.cn: 如今,视频博客比传统的日记更实用,尤其是受到年轻人的欢迎。

examples.en: And it really had nowhere to go.
examples.cn: 因为确实无处可去。

examples.en: The winning number in the lottery was announced by the media.
examples.cn: 彩票中奖号码被媒体公布了。

examples.en: Is Li Ping's mother a nurse or a doctor?
examples.cn: 李平的母亲是护士还是医生?

examples.en: Drivers should obey traffic rules to ensure the safety of themselves and others.
examples.cn: 司机应该遵守交通规则,以确保自己和他人的安全。

examples.en: It would be equally important for Sister Badgery to observe.
examples.cn: 察言观色对巴杰莉修女来说也同等重要。

examples.en: He wanted to look for an occupation suited to his abilities.
examples.cn: 他想找个与自身能力相配的职业。

examples.en: The world really has one big ocean.
examples.cn: 世界上其实只有一个海洋。

examples.en: I woke up at four o'clock this morning.
examples.cn: 今天早上我4点钟就醒了。

examples.en: Would you tell me what you did on the evening of 8th October?
examples.cn: 能否告诉我10月8日晚上你在干嘛?

examples.en: They had two children of their own.
examples.cn: 他们有两个自己的孩子。

translations.translation: 离开,走开;断掉(水、电等);完,光

examples.en: We said good-bye, then he turned and walked off without another word.
examples.cn: 我们说了声“再见”,他便转身离去,没再说一句话。

examples.en: I'm sorry we were cut off.
examples.cn: 抱歉!刚刚电话断了。

translations.translation: 提供;主动提出;自愿给予

examples.en: Today's special offer gives you a choice of three destinations.
examples.cn: 今天推出的特价线路有3个目的地可供选择。

examples.en: Jack is such a forgetful fellow, for he always leaves this or that at the office.
examples.cn: 杰克是一个健忘的家伙,因为他总把这个或那个东西落在办公室。

expand: officer n. 官员,办事员,长官
official n. (公司、团体或政府的)官员
adj. 官方的,政府的;官员的

examples.en: An officer is receiving her.
examples.cn: 一位官员正在接待她。

examples.en: A senior UN official hopes to visit China this month.
examples.cn: 一位联合国高级官员希望于本月访问中国。

examples.en: It is official policy line.
examples.cn: 这是官方的政策路线。

examples.en: Kitty is such an honest student that she is often praised by her teachers.
examples.cn: 姬蒂是这样一位诚实的学生,她经常受到老师的表扬。

examples.en: Oil is liquid.
examples.cn: 石油是液体。

examples.en: It's natural for us to become more forgetful when we get old.
examples.cn: 当我们老了,我们变得更健忘,这是自然的。

examples.en: He is an Olympic champion.
examples.cn: 他是一位奥运会冠军。

translations.translation: (穿、放...)上;(水、电等)接通;进行下去

examples.en: What great fun it is to chat with our friends on the Internet!
examples.cn: 在互联网上与我们的朋友聊天多么有趣啊!

examples.en: He arrived at the airport on time.
examples.cn: 他准时到达机场。

examples.en: Mary once dreamed of Snow White.
examples.cn: 玛丽有一次梦到了白雪公主。

examples.en: He was once unlucky in his work.
examples.cn: 他一度工作不顺利。

examples.en: He is one who never troubles about his personal interests.
examples.cn: 他是一个从不计较个人利益的人。

examples.en: It's true that our life has become much easier with the growth of online payment services.
examples.cn: 随着在线支付服务的发展,我们的生活确实变得方便多了。

examples.en: There is only a little milk.
examples.cn: 只有一点牛奶了。

examples.en: His spoon dropped onto the ground.
examples.cn: 他的汤勺掉到了地上。

translations.translation: 开着的,开口的;敞开的;营业中的

examples.en: "Please open your mouth wide, so that I can examine your teeth easily," said the dentist.
examples.cn: 牙医说:"请张大嘴,便于我检查你的牙齿"。

examples.en: Doctor Lin left in a hurry to operate on a wounded young man just now.
examples.cn: 林医生刚才匆匆赶去为一个受伤的年轻男子动手术。

expand: operator n. 电话员;接线员

examples.en: The doctor performed an operation on her brain last week.
examples.cn: 上周医生为她做了脑部手术。

examples.en: In my opinion, Tim doesn't write English as clearly as his sister.
examples.cn: 在我看来,蒂姆的英文没有他妹妹写得清楚。

translations.translation: 在...对面的;相对的;对立的

examples.en: I should have written the notes in the opposite order.
examples.cn: 我本应按相反的顺序记笔记的。

examples.en: Take the exam carefully, or you won't get full marks.
examples.cn: 考试时要仔细,否则你就得不到满分。

examples.en: Orange juice contains things which help keep you healthy.
examples.cn: 橘子汁里含有益于健康的东西。

examples.en: The commander gave his order to the soldier.
examples.cn: 指挥官向士兵下达命令。

examples.en: I have ordered an egg for you.
examples.cn: 我已经帮你点了个蛋。

examples.en: I just want an ordinary car.
examples.cn: 我只想要一辆普通的车。

examples.en: The United Nations Organization consists of over 190 nations.
examples.cn: 联合国组织由190多个国家组成。

examples.en: Our school will organize a sightseeing to Hong Kong Ocean Park.
examples.cn: 我们学校将组织一次到香港海洋公园的游览。

examples.en: You cannot do everything as well as certain other people do.
examples.cn: 你不可能把每一件事都做得和其他一些人一样好。

examples.en: He ought to keep his promise.
examples.cn: 他应该遵守诺言。

examples.en: Let's go out for a walk.
examples.cn: 我们出去散散步吧。

examples.en: The streetlights were out after the storm.
examples.cn: 暴风雨过后,路灯都熄灭了。

examples.en: I like outdoor sports.
examples.cn: 我喜欢室外运动。

translations.translation: 远足;郊游;(集体)外出游玩(或学习等)

examples.en: We were just thinking of an outing, but the odds were against us and it began to rain.
examples.cn: 我们正想去郊游,不料天公不作美,下起雨来了。

examples.en: For example, you might want to speak about your interests and hobbies outside school.
examples.cn: 比如说,你可能想说说你在校外的兴趣和爱好。

examples.en: She took the pie out of the oven.
examples.cn: 她将馅饼从烤箱中拿出来。

examples.en: We live over a small bookstore.
examples.cn: 我们住在一家小书店的楼上。

examples.en: We all know that success in study mainly depends on one's own effort.
examples.cn: 我们都知道学习的成功主要取决于自己的努力。

examples.en: He owns three cars.
examples.cn: 他有3辆汽车。

expand: owner n. 拥有者;物主;主人

examples.en: Who is the owner of that motorcycle?
examples.cn: 谁是那辆摩托车的主人?

examples.en: He visited Pacific Islands yesterday.
examples.cn: 他昨天访问了太平洋岛屿。

examples.en: The tourist carried a pack on his back.
examples.cn: 观光旅行者背了个包。

examples.en: Do the exercises on page ten.
examples.cn: 做第10页上的练习。

examples.en: He has a pain in his stomach.
examples.cn: 他胃痛。

examples.en: Have you moved into the new house?
examples.cn: 你搬进新房了吗?

expand: painting n. 画,油画,水彩画

examples.en: There is a beautiful painting on the wall in each room of my house.
examples.cn: 我住所里每个房间的墙上都有一幅美丽的画。

examples.en: This pair of shoes fits me well.
examples.cn: 这双鞋我穿很合脚。

examples.en: In ancient times, many palaces were built in Beijing, Xi'an and Nanjing.
examples.cn: 在古代,北京、西安和南京建有许多宫殿。

examples.en: She was pale with fear.
examples.cn: 她吓得脸色发白。

examples.en: The panda attracted many children.
examples.cn: 那只熊猫吸引了不少孩子。

translations.translation: (不可数)纸;(可数)报纸;考卷;文件

examples.en: He wrote a number on a piece of paper.
examples.cn: 他在一张纸上写了一个数字。

examples.en: I read the news in the papers.
examples.cn: 我在报纸上看到了这则消息。

examples.en: Peter will cook for his parents when the International Day of Families comes.
examples.cn: “国际家庭日”到来时,彼得将为他的父母做饭。

examples.en: Paris is the capital of France.
examples.cn: 巴黎是法国首都。

examples.en: Mr. Smith thought the Century Park was the second largest in Shanghai.
examples.cn: 史密斯先生认为,世纪公园是上海第二大公园。

examples.en: What an important part computers have played in our daily life!
examples.cn: 计算机在我们的日常生活中扮演着多么重要的角色啊!

examples.en: They were partners in crime.
examples.cn: 他俩是同谋。

examples.en: The family are having a party to celebrate their child's fifth birthday.
examples.cn: 这户人家正在举行一个聚会,庆祝他们孩子的5周岁生日。

examples.en: He passed the ball to Edwards.
examples.cn: 他把球传给了爱德华。

phrase.cn: 传递;转交;(用后)递给,传给

examples.en: People have different interpretations of the passage.
examples.cn: 人们对这一段文字有不同的解释。

examples.en: This bus can carry fifty passengers.
examples.cn: 这辆公交车可载50名乘客。

examples.en: A person who travels abroad must carry a passport.
examples.cn: 出国旅行要携带护照。

examples.en: I arrived at half past ten.
examples.cn: 我10点半到的。

examples.en: The earlier the treatment is given, the more likely the patient is to recover.
examples.cn: 病人越早接受治疗,康复的可能性就越大。

examples.en: He's a very patient man.
examples.cn: 他是个很有耐心的人。

translations.translation: 付钱,给...报酬;(与某些名词结合使用,表示将要做或付出某事物)

examples.en: Mr. Fermont couldn't believe that his wife paid $10,000 for just a handbag.
examples.cn: 费尔蒙先生不敢相信他的妻子花一万美元买了一个手提包。

examples.en: The students have three P.E. lessons a week.
examples.cn: 学生们一周有3节体育课。

examples.en: We live in peace with our neighbours.
examples.cn: 我们与邻居和睦相处。

examples.en: The pear is a delicious fruit and I like it very much.
examples.cn: 梨是一种美味的水果,我非常喜欢。

examples.en: The necklace is made of natural pearls.
examples.cn: 这条项链是用天然珍珠做成的。

examples.en: Students are required to write their exercises in pen.
examples.cn: 学生被要求用钢笔做练习。

examples.en: Who has taken my pencil away? I used it minutes ago.
examples.cn: 谁拿了我的铅笔?几分钟前我还在用呢。

examples.en: It is reported that more than two thousand people have been killed in this big earthquake.
examples.cn: 据报道,在这次的大地震中死亡人数已超过两千人。

examples.en: The lunch is $3.50 per person.
examples.cn: 午餐费是每人3.5美元。

examples.en: Twenty percent of the products are exported.
examples.cn: 百分之二十的产品外销。

examples.en: Her acting is really perfect.
examples.cn: 她的演技真到了炉火纯青的境界。

examples.en: The performance of Class A students is much better than that of Class B students.
examples.cn: A班学生的表演明显优于B班学生。

examples.en: Perhaps I can help you.
examples.cn: 也许我能帮你忙。

examples.en: Nobody would like to make friends with those dishonest persons.
examples.cn: 没有人会和那些不诚实的人交朋友。

expand: personal adj. 个人的;私人的

examples.en: It's all a matter of personal taste.
examples.cn: 这纯粹是个人的品味问题。

examples.en: Many people like to keep pet dogs because dogs will love people faithfully forever.
examples.cn: 很多人都喜欢养宠物狗,因为狗会永远对人忠实。

examples.en: Doug's 14-year-old son Jamie answered the phone.
examples.cn: 道格14岁的儿子杰米接了电话。

examples.en: We took many photos at Grandpa's birthday party.
examples.cn: 我们在爷爷的生日聚会上拍了很多照片。

examples.en: Playing basketball is one form of physical exercise.
examples.cn: 打篮球是体育锻炼的一种形式。

examples.en: Physics isn't so difficult. You needn't be disappointed. I'm sure you'll pass it next time.
examples.cn: 物理不是那么难。你不必感到失望。我确信你下一次会通过。

examples.en: Alice loves music. Every day she practises playing the piano for an hour.
examples.cn: 爱丽丝热爱音乐。她每天练习弹钢琴一个小时。

examples.en: Would you please help me pick up the umbrella on the floor?
examples.cn: 请你帮我把地板上的伞拾起来好吗?

examples.en: If it doesn't rain tomorrow, we will have a picnic in the park.
examples.cn: 如果明天不下雨,我们就去公园野餐。

examples.en: I had a picture taken this morning.
examples.cn: 今天上午我请人给我拍了张照片。

translations.translation: 一块(片、张、件、段...);碎片;碎块;部件

examples.en: Could you give me a piece of paper?
examples.cn: 你能给我一张纸吗?

examples.en: He keeps pigs as a career.
examples.cn: 他以养猪为业。

examples.en: Why do I have to take all these pills?
examples.cn: 我为什么非得服下所有这些药丸?

examples.en: Robin was once a fighter pilot during World War II.
examples.cn: 罗宾在二战期间曾当过战斗机飞行员。

examples.en: The secretary pinned the papers together.
examples.cn: 秘书把文件钉在一起。

examples.en: She drank a cup of pineapple juice.
examples.cn: 她喝了一杯菠萝汁。

examples.en: She was dressed in pink.
examples.cn: 她穿着粉红色的衣服。

examples.en: They were the pioneers of the American West.
examples.cn: 他们是美国西部的开拓者。

examples.en: She never asked for pity before.
examples.cn: 她过去从未乞求怜悯。

examples.en: He likes to eat pizzas.
examples.cn: 他喜欢吃比萨饼。

examples.en: There are many interesting places for children everywhere.
examples.cn: 有许多有趣的地方供孩子们玩。

examples.en: Two-thirds of people said yes to the new plan.
examples.cn: 三分之二的人同意这个新计划。

examples.en: The pilot landed the plane safely at its home airport.
examples.cn: 飞行员将飞机安全地降落在驻地机场。

examples.en: The planets move around the sun.
examples.cn: 行星绕着太阳转。

examples.en: People had planted a lot of trees along the lake by the end of last month.
examples.cn: 到上个月底,人们沿湖种植了很多树木。

examples.en: The company sells plastic products.
examples.cn: 这家公司出售塑料制品。

examples.en: He had a plate of beef for lunch.
examples.cn: 他午餐吃了一盘牛肉。

examples.en: I must put my thoughts together before I go on the platform.
examples.cn: 在走上讲台讲演之前,我要把我的思绪整理一下。

examples.en: Although Yao Ming has made himself known to the whole world for his talent in playing basketball, he still stays very humble.
examples.cn: 虽然姚明已经让全世界知道他有打篮球的天赋,他依然非常谦虚。

expand: player n. 运动员;选手;演奏者

examples.en: People crowded round the player with congratulations.
examples.cn: 人们簇拥着那个运动员向他祝贺。

examples.en: You can find him on the playground, I think.
examples.cn: 我想你去操场能找到他。

examples.en: His sister sings well. She has a pleasant voice.
examples.cn: 他的姐姐唱歌唱得很好。她有一副悦耳的嗓音。

expand: pleased adj. 感到高兴的;感到满意的
pleasure n. 高兴;愉快;快乐

examples.en: Will you please tell him the news when you see him?
examples.cn: 当你看到他时,请告诉他这个消息好吗?

translations.translation: 感到高兴的;感到满意的

examples.en: We are very pleased with our new house.
examples.cn: 我们对自己的新居很满意。

examples.en: Mrs. Zhou always helps her students with great pleasure.
examples.cn: 周老师总是非常乐意帮助她的学生。

examples.en: The garden was blooming with colourful flowers in plenty.
examples.cn: 花园里开满了五颜六色的花。

examples.en: Five plus two equals seven.
examples.cn: 5加2等于7。

examples.en: It's 1:00 p.m. now.
examples.cn: 现在是下午1点。

examples.en: The policeman made the thief turn out his pockets.
examples.cn: 警察叫小偷把口袋都翻出来。

examples.en: This poem is so wonderful.
examples.cn: 这首诗太棒了。

translations.translation: 点;得分;分数;小数点;尖端

examples.en: It's rude to point your fingers at people.
examples.cn: 用手指指人是不礼貌的。

examples.en: We used a branch as a fishing pole.
examples.cn: 我们用树枝做钓竿。

examples.en: The old man was thankful to the policeman who found the lost car for him.
examples.cn: 这位老人感激警察找到了他丢失的汽车。

examples.en: I've never seen such a polite clerk.
examples.cn: 我从未见过这样有礼貌的店员。

examples.en: "Would you please stop smoking?" the little girl said to the man politely.
examples.cn: 小女孩有礼貌地对那个男子说:‘请你不要吸烟好吗?’

examples.en: Politics was one of his university subjects.
examples.cn: 政治学是他大学的课程之一。

examples.en: The environment will be seriously polluted if people don't take any action.
examples.cn: 如果人们不采取任何行动,环境将受到严重污染。

examples.en: All the students in Shanghai should help fight against pollution to protect the environment.
examples.cn: 上海所有的学生都应该为保护环境与污染作斗争。

examples.en: After the heavy rain there were pools on the road.
examples.cn: 大雨过后路上有一些小水塘。

examples.en: My family used to be poor.
examples.cn: 我家过去很穷。

translations.translation: 流行的;大众喜爱的;广受欢迎的;当红的

examples.en: City Walk has become extremely popular between local people in Shanghai.
examples.cn: 城市漫步在上海当地人中变得极为流行。

examples.en: More nursing homes will be built for the aging population in the next few years.
examples.cn: 在未来几年将建造更多的养老院,以应对人口老龄化。

examples.en: How much pork do you need to make dumplings for the family and the guests?
examples.cn: 为家人和客人包饺子你需要多少猪肉?

examples.en: Is such a thing possible?
examples.cn: 这种事可能吗?

examples.en: Mary is good at writing. She will possibly be a reporter in the future.
examples.cn: 玛丽擅长写作。她将来可能会成为一名记者。

examples.en: If you could get the book, please send it to me by post.
examples.cn: 如果你能弄到那本书,请邮寄给我。

examples.en: He sent me a postcard from the United Nations.
examples.cn: 他从联合国给我寄来一张明信片。

examples.en: He put up a poster advertising the circus.
examples.cn: 他贴出了一张宣传马戏团的海报。

examples.en: His ambition is to be a postman.
examples.cn: 他的志向是成为一名邮递员。

examples.en: Most of the flower pots were moved into the house by Mrs. Green last night.
examples.cn: 昨晚大多数的花盆都被格林太太搬进了房子里。

examples.en: They bought some fresh potatoes at the supermarket yesterday.
examples.cn: 昨天他们在超市买了一些新鲜的土豆。

examples.en: Will you change me five ten-pound notes?
examples.cn: 你给我换5张10英镑的纸币好吗?

translations.translation: 电源;能源;动力;电力;电力供应

examples.en: They have built three nuclear power stations this year.
examples.cn: 今年他们建造了3座核电站。

expand: powerful adj. 强大的;强有力的

examples.en: Her voice was so powerful that it reached every corner of the concert hall.
examples.cn: 她的声音如此响亮,以至于传到了音乐厅的每个角落。

examples.en: Only practice can achieve mastery.
examples.cn: 只有实践才能达到精通。

examples.en: His good behavior deserves praise.
examples.cn: 他的好品行值得表扬。

examples.en: Time is precious.
examples.cn: 时间是宝贵的。

examples.en: People cannot predict how things will pan out.
examples.cn: 人们无法预料事情会有什么样的结果。

translations.translation: 宁愿(选择),更喜欢,喜欢...多于...

examples.en: I prefer running to swimming.
examples.cn: 比起游泳,我更喜欢跑步。

examples.en: We are preparing for the party.
examples.cn: 我们在为派对做准备。

examples.en: John gave Mary a wonderful present on her thirtieth birthday.
examples.cn: 在玛丽30周岁生日时,约翰给了她一个精美的礼物。

examples.en: The president will give a speech on the morning of the National Day.
examples.cn: 总统将在国庆节的上午发表讲话。

examples.en: Please press this button.
examples.cn: 请按这个按钮。

examples.en: She closed her eyes and pretended to be asleep.
examples.cn: 她闭上眼睛装睡。

examples.en: What a pretty doll it is!
examples.cn: 多漂亮的洋娃娃!

examples.en: He did pretty well on his exam.
examples.cn: 他考试考得相当不错。

translations.translation: 防止,预防;阻止,阻挡,阻碍

examples.en: How to prevent disease?
examples.cn: 怎么预防疾病?

examples.en: Nowadays people complain that food prices are higher than before.
examples.cn: 现在人们都抱怨食品价格比以前高了。

examples.en: She studies in a primary school.
examples.cn: 她在上小学。

examples.en: Print the word in italics.
examples.cn: 用斜体印刷这个字。

examples.en: The building over there is a prison.
examples.cn: 那边的那幢建筑是一座监狱。

examples.en: Some young people are now rich enough to buy private cars.
examples.cn: 现在有一些年轻人有能力买私家车。

examples.en: Jessie got the top prize in the writing competition. She felt very excited.
examples.cn: 杰西获得了征文比赛的最高奖项。她感到非常兴奋。

translations.translation: 很可能发生(或存在等)的;很可能的;大概的

examples.en: It is probable that he told her everything.
examples.cn: 很可能他把一切都告诉她了。

expand: probably adv. 很可能,大概,或许

examples.en: John probably told his father all about the matter.
examples.cn: 约翰很可能把这一切都告诉了他父亲。

translations.translation: 棘手的问题,难题,困难;习题

examples.en: I'm sure you will succeed in working out the problem unless you give up.
examples.cn: 我相信你会成功解决这个问题,除非你放弃。

examples.en: How fast does the computer process the data?
examples.cn: 这台计算机处理数据有多快?

examples.en: The new factory will produce goods for export.
examples.cn: 这家新工厂将生产出口产品。

examples.en: This plan was the product of many hours of careful thought.
examples.cn: 这个计划是经过长时间仔细思考的产物。

examples.en: After graduation, she became a professional accountant.
examples.cn: 毕业以后,她成为一名专业会计。

translations.translation: 节目(单);项目;计划;方案;活动安排;【计】程序

examples.en: I love the programme "Schools in students' eyes" made by Shanghai Educational TV Station.
examples.cn: 我喜欢由上海教育电视台制作的《学生眼中的学校》这个节目。

examples.en: You can make much progress in your study if you work hard.
examples.cn: 如果努力学习,你就会取得很大进步。

translations.translation: 工程;课程;作业;项目;规划

examples.en: Linda did her project on Chinese traditional food far more carefully than me.
examples.cn: 琳达在做中国传统食物这个项目时,远远比我仔细。

examples.en: Not only did he make a promise, but also he kept it.
examples.cn: 他不仅作出了许诺,而且履行了诺言。

examples.en: He can pronounce this word correctly.
examples.cn: 他能正确地念这个字。

examples.en: Healthy food is very important to help our minds work properly.
examples.cn: 健康食品对于我们大脑的正常运行非常重要。

expand: proper adj. 正确的;恰当的

examples.en: It's necessary for us to know how to protect ourselves in an earthquake.
examples.cn: 我们有必要知道在地震中如何保护自己。

examples.en: That famous hotel is proud of its spotless rooms, tasty food and good service.
examples.cn: 那家著名的酒店以其一尘不染的房间、美味的食物和优质的服务引以为豪。

examples.en: Let time prove this friendship.
examples.cn: 让时间证明这份友情。

examples.en: Most people are familiar with the proverb: Rome was not built in a day.
examples.cn: 大多数人都熟悉这个谚语:罗马不是一天建成的。

examples.en: To protect the environment, supermakets don't provide free plastic bags for shoppers.
examples.cn: 为了保护环境,超市不再为顾客提供免费塑料袋。

examples.en: Mary's father rarely smokes in public places, does he?
examples.cn: 玛丽的父亲很少在公共场所抽烟,是吗?

examples.en: By the age of ten, the little girl had published her first collection of poems. She's now very famous.
examples.cn: 这个小女孩在10岁的时候已经出版了她的第一本诗集。她现在很出名。

examples.en: Many old houses around our school will be pulled down next year and a large green area will appear.
examples.cn: 明年我们学校周围许多旧房子要被拆除,将出现一片大型的绿化区域。

examples.en: The main purpose of the charity project is to offer help to homeless people.
examples.cn: 这个慈善项目的主要目的是帮助无家可归的人。

translations.translation: 推动(人或物);移动(身体部位)

examples.en: Push your chair in gently.
examples.cn: 轻轻地把你的椅子推进去。

examples.en: One of their tasks is to put an ice radar in the station.
examples.cn: 他们的任务之一是把冰雷达放在雷达站里。

examples.en: In production, we demand not only quantity but also quality.
examples.cn: 我们的产品不但要求数量而且要求质量。

examples.en: It's a quarter to seven.
examples.cn: 现在是6点45分。

examples.en: The queen was sad.
examples.cn: 皇后很伤心。

examples.en: Well done! You have answered all the questions correctly.
examples.cn: 干得好!你已正确回答了所有的问题。

examples.en: Among the boys, Tom is the quickest to learn new things.
examples.cn: 在男孩中,学习新事物学得最快的是汤姆。

expand: quickly adv. 很快地;迅速地

examples.en: When he heard a cry for help, he ran out as quickly as he could.
examples.cn: 一听到呼救声,他就尽快跑了出来。

examples.en: I'm going to move somewhere quiet. It's too noisy in our neighbourhood.
examples.cn: 我打算搬到一个安静的地方。小区太吵了。

examples.en: The patient lay on his bed quietly when the doctor came to examine him.
examples.cn: 当医生来给这位病人检查时,他静静地躺在床上。

examples.en: This arrangement is quite satisfactory, so far as I am concerned.
examples.cn: 就我来说,这样的安排相当好。

examples.en: We'll have a quiz at the end of class.
examples.cn: 下课前我们将进行一次测试。

examples.en: Are you going to race your horse at Newmarket next week?
examples.cn: 你准备让你的马参加下周在纽马克特的赛马会吗?

examples.en: Father bought her a stereo radio.
examples.cn: 父亲给她买了一台立体声收音机。

examples.en: The railway is still under construction.
examples.cn: 这条铁路仍在建设之中。

examples.en: In fact, there isn't so much rain in the city as they think.
examples.cn: 事实上,这座城市不像他们想的那样有这么多的雨水。

expand: rainy adj. 有雨的;多雨的

examples.en: Most tropical areas have rainy and dry seasons.
examples.cn: 大多数热带地区有季和旱季。

translations.translation: 举起,使升高,提升;饲养,抚养;筹钱,筹集

examples.en: The government's decision on building a factory in the city centre has raised many questions among the local people.
examples.cn: 政府决定在城市中心建造一家工厂,这在当地人中已经引发了许多质疑。

examples.en: People in western countries rarely talk loudly in public, do they?
examples.cn: 在西方国家,人们很少在公共场所大声说话,是吗?

translations.translation: 相当,颇;宁可;反而;有点儿,稍微

examples.en: I'm feeling rather sleepy.
examples.cn: 我感到十分困倦。

examples.en: My uncle will send me postcards and stamps after he reaches France.
examples.cn: 我的叔叔到达法国后,会给我寄一些明信片和邮票。

examples.en: It's easy to memorise the words if we know how to read them correctly.
examples.cn: 如果我们知道如何正确地读出这些单词,就很容易记住它们了。

translations.translation: 准备好的;准备完毕的;乐于

examples.en: He is ready for the trip.
examples.cn: 他已准备好去旅行。

examples.en: The real value of the book lies in its wonderful characterisation.
examples.cn: 这本书真正的价值在于精彩的人物塑造。

expand: really adv. 真正地,确实;事实上
realize v. 认识到;实现(= be aware of)

examples.en: If you want to realize your dream, study hard from now on.
examples.cn: 如果你想实现自己的梦想,从现在开始就要努力学习。

examples.en: It's really impossible for a child of five to take care of himself.
examples.cn: 要5岁儿童自己照顾自己,这真的是不可能的。

examples.en: That is the reason why we must go now.
examples.cn: 那就是我们现在必须走的理由。

examples.en: The house was rebuilt after the fire.
examples.cn: 这房子是火灾后重建的。

examples.en: By the end of last month, Mrs. Lin had received many interesting comic strips created by the students.
examples.cn: 到上月底,林老师收到了许多由学生创作的有趣的漫画。

examples.en: There have been many changes in our school in recent years.
examples.cn: 近几年,我们学校发生了许多变化。

examples.en: I hear that her uncle has bought a new flat in the city centre recently.
examples.cn: 我听说她的叔叔最近在市中心买了一套新房子。

examples.en: She had changed so much that I could hardly recognize her.
examples.cn: 她的变化这么大,我简直认不出来了。

examples.en: Several world records were broken by Bolt at the Olympics.
examples.cn: 博尔特在奥运会上打破了多项世界纪录。

examples.en: We should recycle garbage, not burn it.
examples.cn: 我们应该回收利用垃圾,而不是焚烧。

examples.en: He was wearing a white shirt and a red tie.
examples.cn: 他穿着一件白衬衫,系了一条红领带。

examples.en: We have reduced the number of classes from eight to six.
examples.cn: 我们已将班级数量由8个减少到6个。

examples.en: The author does not give references.
examples.cn: 作者没有注明参考(所引资料的)出处。

examples.en: I don't know why he refused the job offer.
examples.cn: 我不明白他为什么拒绝那份工作。

examples.en: There are two most famous and popular programs which have regular performances in Shanghai Circus World.
examples.cn: 有两个最著名、最受欢迎的节目定期在上海马戏城演出。

expand: regularly adv. 规则地;经常地

examples.en: She found it impossible to extricate herself from the relationship.
examples.cn: 她发现自己不可能从这种关系中解脱出来。

examples.en: Today we visited our relative.
examples.cn: 今天我们探望了我们的亲戚。

examples.en: Sam needs to relax himself, so he is looking forward to a holiday.
examples.cn: 萨姆需要放松自己,所以他期待着假期。

expand: relaxed adj. 轻松的,自在的

examples.en: It helps us release anxious thoughts.
examples.cn: 它能帮助我们释放焦虑情绪。

examples.en: You can always rely on Jim, he won't fail you.
examples.cn: 你可以永远依靠吉姆,他不会让你失望的。

examples.en: The famous singer died, but her sweet voice will be remembered for ever.
examples.cn: 这位著名歌手去世了,但她甜美的声音将永远被铭记。

examples.en: He reminded me that I ought to do it at once.
examples.cn: 他提醒我应该现在就去做这件事。

examples.en: The house is in need of repair.
examples.cn: 那幢房子需要整修。

examples.en: Though I repeated the phone number many times, the foreigner still couldn't write it down.
examples.cn: 虽然我把电话号码重复了好多次,这个外国人还是不能把它写下来。

examples.en: He never replied to the letters.
examples.cn: 他从来都不回信。

translations.translation: 报道;报告;成绩单;(新闻)报道;调查报告

examples.en: She has given us a progress report on how the project is going.
examples.cn: 她给我们作了关于项目进程的报告。

examples.en: The reporter described the accident in detail.
examples.cn: 记者详尽地描述了那起意外事件。

examples.en: the People's Republic of China
examples.cn: 中华人民共和国

examples.en: A person can do what he wants to do, but he can't require to gain what he wants.
examples.cn: 一个人可以想干什么就干什么,却不能想要什么就得到什么。

examples.en: The historical background to the play has been very carefully and thoroughly researched.
examples.cn: 已对这个剧本的历史背景进行了细致全面的研究。

examples.en: This country is rich in natural resources.
examples.cn: 该国自然资源丰富。

examples.en: I respect him for his diligence.
examples.cn: 我敬佩他的勤奋。

examples.en: She has received a response from that college to her application.
examples.cn: 她已经收到那所大学对她申请的答复。

expand: respond v. 作出反应;回应

examples.en: We need to take responsibility for looking after our own health.
examples.cn: 我们必须对自己的健康负责。

expand: responsible adj. 负责的;有责任的

examples.en: Being responsible means taking ownership of your mistakes and learning from them.
examples.cn: 有责任感意味着要对自己的错误负责,并从中吸取教训。

translations.translation: 休息;剩余部分;其余的人(物)

examples.en: The doctor advised him to take a rest for a few days.
examples.cn: 医生建议他休息几天。

examples.en: I shall leave the restaurant unless the waiter comes soon.
examples.cn: 除非服务员马上来,否则我就离开饭店。

examples.en: Remember, the harder you work, the more good results you will get.
examples.cn: 记住,你越努力工作,你越会得到好的结果。

examples.en: The retired workers receive money from the government till they die.
examples.cn: 退休工人从政府那里领取养老金直到去世为止。

examples.en: He returned the books to the library yesterday.
examples.cn: 他昨天把书还给了图书馆。

examples.en: The same water was reused after chemical treatment.
examples.cn: 原来的水经过化学处理之后被再度利用。

expand: reusable adj. 可重复使用的;可再次使用的

examples.en: The college published a drama review.
examples.cn: 学院出版了一份戏剧评论刊物。

translations.translation: 奖励;奖赏;报酬;报答,回报

examples.en: He was given the job as a reward for running a successful leadership bid.
examples.cn: 因为成功组织了领导职位竞选活动,他得到了这份工作。

examples.en: The southerners prefer rice and the northerners prefer food made from flour.
examples.cn: 南方人比较喜欢吃米饭,北方人爱吃面食。

translations.translation: 富裕的,有钱的;味道浓的;重油的;丰富的

examples.en: A lot of people think that happiness is about being rich, but I disagree.
examples.cn: 很多人认为幸福就是富有,但我不同意。

examples.en: It's not easy to rid oneself of a habit.
examples.cn: 要改掉一个人的习惯是不容易的。

translations.translation: 乘车旅行;(乘车或骑马的)短途旅程

examples.en: Now my father rides his bike to work every day instead of driving.
examples.cn: 现在我的父亲每天骑自行车去上班而不是开车去。

translations.translation: 对的,正确的;恰当的;右边的
正确地;恰恰;向右,在右边

examples.en: I'll try to do whatever is right.
examples.cn: 只要是正当的事,我都尽力去做。

examples.en: It's quite late. We'd better go home by taxi right now.
examples.cn: 太晚了,我们最好现在打车回家。

examples.en: Let's hurry up. The electric bell is ringing.
examples.cn: 我们快点。电铃响了。

examples.en: The river is rising after the rain.
examples.cn: 雨后河水涨了起来。

examples.en: These factories are trying their best not to pollute the river any longer.
examples.cn: 这些工厂正在尽力不再污染河流。

examples.en: We should drive carefully on the road.
examples.cn: 在道路上我们应该小心驾驶。

examples.en: You've made a fire fit to roast an ox.
examples.cn: 你生的火很旺,足以烤一头牛了。

examples.en: She worked like a robot.
examples.cn: 她工作起来如同一个机器人。

examples.en: Astronauts have brought back specimens of rock from the moon.
examples.cn: 宇航员从月球带回了岩石标本。

examples.en: She prefers rock music to classical.
examples.cn: 比起古典乐,她更喜欢摇滚乐。

examples.en: This space rocket carries two satellites.
examples.cn: 这枚宇宙火箭搭载了两颗卫星。

examples.en: She prefers to play comic roles.
examples.cn: 她更喜欢扮演喜剧角色。

examples.en: This is a three-metre-high room.
examples.cn: 这是一个3米高的房间。

examples.en: The roots of this plant go deep.
examples.cn: 这种植物的根扎得很深。

examples.en: They tied the ship to the quay with ropes.
examples.cn: 他们用绳子把船拴在码头上。

examples.en: He picked her a rose.
examples.cn: 他给她采了一朵玫瑰花。

translations.translation: 粗糙的;不平的;风浪急的;令人不舒服的

examples.en: It's just a very rough translation.
examples.cn: 这只是一篇非常粗糙的翻译。

examples.en: The child had a round face.
examples.cn: 那孩子是圆脸。

examples.en: A row of children are standing in front of a row of chairs.
examples.cn: 一排小孩站在一排椅子前。

examples.en: There is a pile of rubbish in the corner of the building.
examples.cn: 在大楼的角落有一堆垃圾。

examples.en: It's very rude of her to leave without telling us.
examples.cn: 她不向我们打声招呼就走了,这是非常无礼的。

examples.en: You should obey the traffic rules.
examples.cn: 你应该遵守交通规则。

examples.en: Rabbits run fast.
examples.cn: 兔子跑得快。

examples.en: He runs a company.
examples.cn: 他经营一家公司。

examples.en: The students rushed into the classroom as soon as the bell rang.
examples.cn: 铃声一响,学生就奔跑进教室。

examples.en: We are very sad and angry to hear that our football team suffered a defeat again.
examples.cn: 听到我们的足球队又输球了,我们非常难过,非常生气。

expand: sadly adv. 悲哀地;忧愁地;令人遗憾地;不幸地

translations.translation: 悲哀地;忧愁地;令人遗憾地;不幸地

examples.en: Sadly, after eight years of marriage they had grown apart.
examples.cn: 不幸的是,结婚8年后,他们的感情日渐淡漠了。

examples.en: Friends are the people you feel safe because you know they care about you.
examples.cn: 朋友就是那些能让你有安全感的人,因为你知道他们关心你。

expand: safely adv. 安全地,平安地
save v. 救,挽救;节省;节约

examples.en: The plane landed safely at last after flying in the storm for about one hour.
examples.cn: 这架飞机在风暴中大约飞行了一个小时以后,最终安全着陆。

examples.en: All pilots are responsible for their passengers' safety.
examples.cn: 所有飞行员都应对乘客的安全负责。

examples.en: He had a steak and a green salad.
examples.cn: 他要了一块牛排和一份生菜色拉。

examples.en: He was engaged at a salary of $1,000 a month.
examples.cn: 他以月薪1000美元受聘。

examples.en: Our school organized a charity sale for the homeless in that area.
examples.cn: 我们学校在该地区为无家可归者组织了一场慈善义卖。

examples.en: Salt occurs naturally in sea water.
examples.cn: 盐天然存在于海水中。

examples.en: The dish is too salty.
examples.cn: 这道菜太咸了。

examples.en: James, Catherine and I have been friends since we were at the same primary school.
examples.cn: 自从我和詹姆斯还有凯瑟琳在同一所小学读书起,我们就一直是朋友。

examples.en: To make a ham sandwich, you put a slice of ham between two slices of bread.
examples.cn: 把一片火腿夹在两片面包之间就做成了火腿三明治。

examples.en: When she had finished her meal, she gave a satisfied smile.
examples.cn: 吃完饭后,她露出了满意的笑容。

expand: satisfy v. 使满意;使满足
satisfying adj. 令人满意的;令人满足的

translations.translation: 令人满意的;令人满足的

examples.en: It's very satisfying to see so many of you here.
examples.cn: 在这里见到大家,我感到非常满意。

examples.en: He went abroad last Saturday.
examples.cn: 他上星期六出国了。

examples.en: The sauce tastes too sweet.
examples.cn: 这酱汁味道太甜。

examples.en: Although the doctors did everything they could to save the sick boy, they failed at last.
examples.cn: 虽然医生们尽力挽救这个生病的孩子,但最终还是失败了。

examples.en: "There's still a long way to go before you succeed," the teacher said to the class.
examples.cn: 老师对全班学生说:"在你们成功之前还有很长的路要走。"

expand: saying n. 谚语,俗语;格言

examples.en: "There's no smoke without fire", as the saying goes.
examples.cn: 常言道:"无风不起浪。"

translations.translation: 时间表;节目表;工作计划;日程安排

examples.en: Because of her busy schedule, it is impossible for her to spend much time traveling.
examples.cn: 由于她的日程安排很紧,她不可能花很多时间旅行。

examples.en: John was seriously injured in the school bus accident.
examples.cn: 约翰在校车事故中受了重伤。

examples.en: Though he is only eight years old, he knows more about science than his father.
examples.cn: 虽然只有8岁,但他比他父亲更了解科学。

examples.en: Mr. Ren, a Chinese scientist, began to study global climate change more than a decade ago.
examples.cn: 中国科学家任先生在10多年前就开始研究全球气候变化。

examples.en: Nick didn't do very well in the final exam, but his scores are better than last year's.
examples.cn: 虽然尼克期末考试考得不是很好,但他的分数比去年要好。

examples.en: You can see him on the TV screen quite often.
examples.cn: 你可以经常在电视屏幕上见到他。

examples.en: We generally go to the sea for our holidays.
examples.cn: 我们通常去海边度假。

examples.en: There's an excellent seafood restaurant near here.
examples.cn: 离这儿不远有一家非常不错的海鲜餐馆。

examples.en: We searched here and there, but could not find her.
examples.cn: 我们到处找她,但还是找不到。

examples.en: Let's go to the seaside at the weekend!
examples.cn: 周末我们去海滨吧!

examples.en: The seasons change, independent of anyone's wishes.
examples.cn: 四季变化不受任何人约束。

examples.en: The teacher made me move my seat to the front of the classroom.
examples.cn: 老师把我的座位换到了教室的前面。

examples.en: Our team gets a second.
examples.cn: 我们队得了第二名。

expand: secondary adj. 中等的;第二的

examples.en: In secondary school, children get more advanced knowledge.
examples.cn: 在中学,孩子获得更深一些的知识。

examples.en: She made no secret of her greed.
examples.cn: 她毫不掩饰自己的贪婪。

examples.en: She is secretary to the master.
examples.cn: 她是校长的秘书。

examples.en: The chapter falls into three sections.
examples.cn: 这一章共分3节。

translations.translation: 看见,看到;领会,理解;拜访,会见;理会

examples.en: The light is on. I see them watching a slide show.
examples.cn: 灯亮着。我看见他们正在看幻灯片。

examples.en: The farmers are scattering seed.
examples.cn: 农夫们在播种。

examples.en: The baby seems to be asleep.
examples.cn: 那婴儿好像是睡着了。

examples.en: I don't like western food. I seldom eat it unless I go to MacDonald with my daughter.
examples.cn: 我不喜欢吃西餐。我很少吃,除非与我的女儿去麦当劳。

examples.en: Which place in the world would you select as your perfect home?
examples.cn: 你会选择世界上哪个地方作为你最理想的安家之地呢?

examples.en: The book written by that writer didn't sell well last year.
examples.cn: 那位作家写的这本书,去年销售情况不好。

examples.en: China first sent scientists to Antarctica in 1980.
examples.cn: 中国在1980年首次派出科学家到南极。

translations.translation: 年长的;高年级的;高级的

examples.en: Honours were automatically awarded to senior officials just because they were senior.
examples.cn: 荣誉顺理成章地授予资深官员,就因为他们资格老。

examples.en: I haven't got a very good sense of direction, so I easily get lost.
examples.cn: 我的方向感很差,因此我容易迷路。

examples.en: Please make a whole sentence when you answer the question.
examples.cn: 回答问题时请说完整的句子。

examples.en: Our school will begin on September 1.
examples.cn: 我们学校将在9月1日开学。

examples.en: If you have a serious disease, such as heart disease, you'd better not travel there.
examples.cn: 如果你有严重的疾病,如心脏疾病,你最好不要去那里。

expand: seriously adv. 严肃地;严重地;认真地

examples.en: The 70-year-old man was seriously ill and died a few months later.
examples.cn: 那个70岁的男子患了重病,几个月后就去世了。

examples.en: The waiter did his best to serve the customers politely and promptly.
examples.cn: 那位服务员尽量礼貌及时地招待顾客。

expand: service n. 服务;公用事业

examples.en: The customers are pleased with the service of the restaurant.
examples.cn: 顾客对这家餐厅的服务很满意。

translations.translation: 释放;安置,摆放;树立(榜样);创造(纪录)
摄影场;一套;电视机;收音机

examples.en: He set an example of wholehearted service to the people.
examples.cn: 他树立了全心全意为人民服务的榜样。

examples.en: The director was impressed with the details of the set.
examples.cn: 导演对场景的细节印象深刻。

examples.en: Both sides are looking for ways to settle their differences.
examples.cn: 双方都在寻求消除分歧的方法。

examples.en: I had lived two doors away from this family for several years.
examples.cn: 我和这户人家是好几年的邻居了,中间就隔着两家。

examples.en: Shaking hands is a traditional way to greet each other in many places.
examples.cn: 在许多地方握手是一种传统的问候方式。

translations.translation: (同I和we连用,表示将来)将要;会;(用来征求意见)...好吗?

examples.en: Shall I get the key to the bike?
examples.cn: 我去拿自行车钥匙好吗?

examples.en: She felt a deep sense of shame.
examples.cn: 她深感羞愧。

examples.en: I keep practising yoga after work because it helps me keep in good shape.
examples.cn: 我下班后坚持练习瑜伽,因为它有助于我保持良好的身材。

examples.en: Ideas are always shared by my students in class.
examples.cn: 在课堂上,学生总是分享各自的想法。

examples.en: The old man used to raise many sheep to make a living in the west of China.
examples.cn: 老人过去常常靠养羊在中国的西部谋生。

examples.en: You may choose any of the toys on the shelf. But only one for each.
examples.cn: 你们可以选择架子上的任何玩具。但每人只能拿一个。

examples.en: The sun shines brightly.
examples.cn: 阳光灿烂。

examples.en: Are you going to America by plane or by ship the day after tomorrow?
examples.cn: 后天你去美国是乘飞机还是坐船?

examples.en: Do you know the man wearing a white shirt?
examples.cn: 你认识那个穿白衬衫的人吗?

examples.en: You don't mind if I take my shoes off, do you?
examples.cn: 你不介意我把鞋子脱了,是吧?

examples.en: It's not available in the shops.
examples.cn: 商店里都没货。

examples.en: He always shopped at that shop.
examples.cn: 他总在那家商店购物。

examples.en: How could you do it in such a short period of time?
examples.cn: 你是怎么在如此短的时间里做到的?

examples.en: Sometimes I am not as brave as I should be.
examples.cn: 有时我表现得不够勇敢。

examples.en: Don't shout at me!
examples.cn: 不要对我大声叫喊!

translations.translation: 给...看,出示;显示;告知;表明

examples.en: My parents showed me some old pictures that brought back sweet memories.
examples.cn: 我的父母给我看了一些能唤起我甜蜜记忆的老照片。

examples.en: She took two showers a day.
examples.cn: 她每天洗两次澡。

examples.en: Lucy shut her eyes.
examples.cn: 露西闭上了眼睛。

examples.en: At first he was a little shy in class, but now he acts more naturally.
examples.cn: 起初他在班里有点害羞,不过现在表现自然多了。

translations.translation: 有病的,患病的;(想)呕吐的,恶心的

examples.en: On the twelfth day, the sick boy came to life.
examples.cn: 在第12天,患病的男孩活过来了。

examples.en: The students have put some flowers on either side of the corridor and hung some nice pictures on the wall.
examples.cn: 学生们在走廊的两边摆了一些花,在墙上挂了一些漂亮的图片。

examples.en: My sight is failing.
examples.cn: 我的视力在下降。

examples.en: Did you do any sightseeing there?
examples.cn: 在那儿你游览观光了没?

examples.en: Many people choose to have a baby in the year of the dragon because dragon is a sign of power and status.
examples.cn: 很多人选择在龙年生孩子,因为龙是权力和地位的象征。

examples.en: A red lamp is often a danger signal.
examples.cn: 红灯常常是危险的信号。

translations.translation: 静的;无声的;不说话的;沉默的

examples.en: He generally keeps silent at a meeting.
examples.cn: 他通常在会上保持沉默。

examples.en: The dress was made of ivory silk.
examples.cn: 这件连衣裙是用象牙色丝绸做成的。

translations.translation: 傻的,愚蠢的;不明事理的

examples.en: That's a silly question.
examples.cn: 那是个愚蠢的问题。

examples.en: The accident was similar to one that happened in 1931.
examples.cn: 这次事故和1931年发生的那起很像。

examples.en: The operation of this machine is simple.
examples.cn: 这台机器的操作很简单。

expand: simply adv. 仅仅;简单地;只

examples.en: Because of the bad service, the restaurant has received a lot of complaints since last December.
examples.cn: 因为糟糕的服务,自去年12月以来这家餐厅已收到许多投诉。

examples.en: How beautifully you sing!
examples.cn: 你唱得多美呀!

examples.en: My mother is a singer in a famous band.
examples.cn: 我妈妈是一个著名乐队的歌手。

examples.en: Never just memorise single English words. Learn by heart the whole sentences and the phrases so we may know how to use the words.
examples.cn: 不要只背单个英语单词,要记住整个句子和词组,这样我们就可以知道如何使用这些单词。

examples.en: Dear Sir, I am very glad and honoured to write to you.
examples.cn: 亲爱的先生,我能给你写信真是感到十分荣幸。

examples.en: She's as clever as her sister is.
examples.cn: 她和她的妹妹一样聪明。

examples.en: The grown-ups will sit at one table and the children at another.
examples.cn: 大人坐一桌,孩子坐另一桌。

examples.en: A troublesome situation has grown up.
examples.cn: 出现了使人感到棘手的局面。

examples.en: I'd like to change this dress for one in a larger size.
examples.cn: 我想把这件衣服换成大号的。

examples.en: I like winter, because I like to skate.
examples.cn: 我喜欢冬天,因为我喜欢滑冰。

examples.en: Finding the main idea in a paragraph is just one of these reading skills.
examples.cn: 在段落里找中心思想只是阅读技能之一。

examples.en: Is it true that drinking much water prevents the skin from drying out?
examples.cn: 多喝水能防止皮肤干燥,这是真的吗?

examples.en: It's a nice skirt.
examples.cn: 这条裙子很漂亮。

examples.en: A bright moving object appeared in the sky at sunset.
examples.cn: 日落时分,天空中出现了一个移动的发亮物体。

examples.en: The boy was too excited to sleep well last night.
examples.cn: 昨晚那个男孩太兴奋了,根本睡不好。

expand: sleepy adj. 有睡意的;困倦的

examples.en: It is impossible for him to finish the job in two hours. He is so slow.
examples.cn: 他的动作是如此缓慢,不可能在2个小时内完成这项工作。

expand: slowly adv. 慢慢地,缓慢地

examples.en: The cars moved slowly because of the heavy snow.
examples.cn: 因为大雪,车辆缓慢地移动。

examples.en: My parents often tell me we should care for small creatures.
examples.cn: 我的父母经常告诉我,我们应该关心小动物。

translations.translation: 灵巧的;聪明的;智能的;机敏的

examples.en: He thinks he's smarter than Sarah.
examples.cn: 他认为他比萨拉聪明。

examples.en: Coffee is ready. How nice it smells! Would you like some?
examples.cn: 咖啡好了。闻起来真香啊!您来点儿吗?

examples.en: When he saw me, he smiled and waved.
examples.cn: 他一看见我,就微笑着朝我挥挥手。

examples.en: The house is full of smoke.
examples.cn: 满屋子都是烟。

examples.en: I only have a snack at lunch time.
examples.cn: 午饭我只吃了点小吃。

examples.en: The mountains were crowned with snow.
examples.cn: 山上积满了雪。

expand: snowy adj. 下雪的;多雪的

examples.en: I liked to walk in fields on snowy days and to see my footprints left behind.
examples.cn: 我喜欢在下雪天走在田野里,看看我留下的脚印。

examples.en: Some kinds of computers are so tiny that people may be unaware of them.
examples.cn: 有些种类的电脑是如此小,以至于人们可能都没有注意到。

translations.translation: 社会上的;社会地位的;社交的;好社交的

examples.en: Team sports help to develop a child's social skills.
examples.cn: 集体体育运动有助于培养孩子的社交能力。

examples.en: Do you think we ought to learn to be useful to the society?
examples.cn: 你是否认为我们应该学着成为对社会有用的人?

examples.en: I like this silk dress, and it feels so soft and comfortable.
examples.cn: 我喜欢这件丝绸连衣裙,它摸上去是这么的柔软舒适。

examples.en: "My father," said Lucie, softly laying her hand on his.
examples.cn: "爸爸,"露西叫了一声,温柔地把手放在他的手上。

examples.en: A soldier must obey his superior officers.
examples.cn: 士兵必须服从上级军官。

examples.en: Finally, they found a solution to the problem.
examples.cn: 最后,他们找到了解决问题的办法。

examples.en: It is very difficult to solve the problem of air pollution.
examples.cn: 解决空气污染问题是非常困难的。

examples.en: Here is some information on the best cities for your studying abroad.
examples.cn: 这儿有最适合您出国留学的一些城市的信息。

examples.en: You needn't tell me about this. Someone sent me a message about it three days ago.
examples.cn: 你不必告诉我了。3天前有人发消息给我说过这件事了。

examples.en: I can't connect my computer to the Internet. There must be something wrong with it.
examples.cn: 我的电脑连不上网。一定是哪里出问题了。

examples.en: We have to admit sometimes the most expensive one is not always the best one.
examples.cn: 我们不得不承认,有时候最贵的并不总是最好的。

examples.en: Her son looked sad when he learned that he hadn't passed the final exam.
examples.cn: 当得知自己没通过期末考试,她的儿子看起来很悲伤。

examples.en: We have learned three English songs since last week.
examples.cn: 自从上个星期以来,我们已经学了3首英文歌曲。

examples.en: We'll have a three-day holiday soon. What about going to Chongming Island?
examples.cn: 不久我们将有3天假期。去崇明岛怎么样?

translations.translation: 对不起的;抱歉的;难过的

examples.en: I'm sorry for giving so much trouble.
examples.cn: 对不起,给你添了这么多麻烦。

examples.en: At the foot of the hill, you can hear nothing but the sound of the running water.
examples.cn: 在山脚下,除了流水声,你什么都听不到。

examples.en: The restaurant serves various soups.
examples.cn: 这家饭店供应各种各样的汤。

examples.en: I'm lost, which direction is south?
examples.cn: 我迷路了,哪个方向是南?

expand: southern adj. 南面的;南部的

examples.en: Linda and her friends had a discussion about space planes.
examples.cn: 琳达和她的朋友们进行了有关太空飞机的讨论。

examples.en: The spaceship went back to the earth successfully.
examples.cn: 宇宙飞船成功地重返地球。

examples.en: He doesn't often read books in the library in his spare time.
examples.cn: 在业余时间他不经常在图书馆看书。

examples.en: Can you tell me who will speak at the class meeting next Monday?
examples.cn: 你能否告诉我下星期一谁将在班会上发言?

examples.en: His accent is quite special.
examples.cn: 他的口音非常特别。

expand: specially adv. 特定地;明确地

examples.en: The scientist gave a lot of speeches on environmental protection.
examples.cn: 这位科学家做了很多关于环境保护的演讲。

examples.en: Our speed averaged out at 50 km an hour.
examples.cn: 我们的平均速度是每小时50公里。

examples.en: He doesn't spend much time on his homework.
examples.cn: 他花在作业上的时间不多。

examples.en: She feeds the baby with a spoon.
examples.cn: 她用汤匙给婴儿喂食。

examples.en: More than two hundred students took part in the school sports meeting yesterday.
examples.cn: 昨日,200多名学生参加了学校运动会。

translations.translation: 延伸;展开;传播;扩散;散布

examples.en: The bird spread its wings.
examples.cn: 鸟儿展开翅膀。

examples.en: I could smell the spring in the air.
examples.cn: 我在空气中闻到了春天的气息。

examples.en: What a wonderful concert they are putting on in the city square!
examples.cn: 他们正在城市广场上演出一场多么美妙的音乐会啊!

examples.en: She is on friendly terms with most of the school staff.
examples.cn: 她和学校大多数员工友好相处。

examples.en: He doesn't need much money for his collection of stamps.
examples.cn: 他集邮不需要很多的钱。

examples.en: We stood because there were no seats.
examples.cn: 没有座位,我们只好站着。

examples.en: The sun is a star.
examples.cn: 太阳是一颗恒星。

examples.en: The shy boy wondered, “How should I start my speech?
examples.cn: 那个害羞的男孩想知道如何开始他的演讲。

translations.translation: 状态;情形;国家;(美国的)州

examples.en: The state for him seems not good.
examples.cn: 他的处境似乎不太好。

examples.en: We must pay taxes to the State.
examples.cn: 我们必须向国家纳税。

examples.en: How far is the train station from your home?
examples.cn: 你家离火车站有多远?

translations.translation: 停留,逗留,待;保持,继续是

examples.en: Did Mary tell you how long she would stay with us?
examples.cn: 玛丽有没有告诉你她要和我们住在一起多久?

examples.en: I ate four steaks yesterday.
examples.cn: 昨天我吃了4块牛排。

examples.en: The suspect admitted stealing the valuable vase after the detective showed him the proof.
examples.cn: 当侦探给这个犯罪嫌疑人看了证据后,他承认偷了贵重的花瓶。

examples.en: Steam can be seen rising from the wet clothes near the fire.
examples.cn: 我们可以看见水蒸气从靠近火的湿衣服中升起。

examples.en: We are too tired and hungry, so our steps are getting slower and slower.
examples.cn: 我们又饿又累,所以我们的脚步越来越慢。

examples.en: What's wrong with this stamp? It won't stick.
examples.cn: 这邮票怎么回事?粘不住了。

expand: stuck adj. 被卡住的,被困住的

examples.en: The fish is still alive.
examples.cn: 这条鱼还是活的。

examples.en: Keep still while I fasten your shoe.
examples.cn: 站着别动,我给你系鞋带。

examples.en: On Christmas Eve I hung up my stocking along with my sisters'.
examples.cn: 圣诞夜,我把我的长筒袜跟姐妹们的挂在了一起。

examples.en: Henry got a stomachache and asked to be excused.
examples.cn: 亨利肚子疼,请求离开一下。

examples.en: Ancient men made tools of stone.
examples.cn: 古人制作了石头工具。

examples.en: Stop complaining about the traffic. Just think about what we can do to improve it.
examples.cn: 别抱怨交通。好好想想,我们能为此做些什么来改善。

examples.en: She opened a hat store in Paris.
examples.cn: 她在巴黎开了一家帽子店。

examples.en: One day we met with a big storm.
examples.cn: 有天我们遇上了一场暴风雨。

examples.en: Mr. Black told us several funny stories at the party last night.
examples.cn: 昨晚在聚会上布莱克先生给我们讲了一些有趣的故事。

translations.translation: 一直地;直;直接地;坦率地

examples.en: Keep the boat in a straight line.
examples.cn: 让船保持直线航行。

examples.en: She was a strange sort of person; I couldn't make her out.
examples.cn: 她这个人有些古怪,我不能理解她。

examples.en: Strawberry is in season this month.
examples.cn: 这个月草莓正当令。

examples.en: I hate the dogs that create a lot of mess in the streets.
examples.cn: 我讨厌狗把街道搞得乱七八糟。

examples.en: Stress may act as a trigger for these illnesses.
examples.cn: 压力可能会成为引发这些疾病的原因。

examples.en: As a student, you have to be strict with yourself.
examples.cn: 作为一名学生,你必须严格要求自己。

examples.en: He's struck by his father.
examples.cn: 他挨了父亲的打。

translations.translation: 强(壮)的;坚固的;强烈的;坚强的

examples.en: Mr. Baker is still very strong in his nineties, and he often goes out for a walk.
examples.cn: 贝克先生90多岁了依然很硬朗,还经常出去散步。

expand: strongly adv. 坚决地;强烈地

examples.en: I was stuck at home with flu.
examples.cn: 感冒把我困在了家中。

examples.en: Students should be taught how to learn by themselves.
examples.cn: 应教导学生如何自学。

examples.en: We can study in the classroom.
examples.cn: 我们可以在教室里学习。

examples.en: Biology is the study of how living things work.
examples.cn: 生物学是研究生物功能的学科。

examples.en: They were stupid not to follow your advice.
examples.cn: 他们不听你的劝告真傻。

examples.en: Each piece of furniture in their home suited the style of the house.
examples.cn: 他家里的每件家具都与房子的风格相配。

translations.translation: 题目;主题;学科;主语;主体

examples.en: The students took the PISA test in three subjects: reading, maths and science.
examples.cn: 学生参加了 PISA3个科目的测试:阅读、数学和科学。

examples.en: You won't succeed unless you put in the effort and stay focused.
examples.cn: 除非你付出努力并保持专注,否则就不会成功。

expand: successful adj. 达到目的的;有成效的;获得成功的

phrase.en: succeed in doing sth. = manage to do sth.

examples.en: The young actor's debut was a great success.
examples.cn: 那位年轻演员的处女秀取得了巨大成功。

translations.translation: 达到目的的;有成效的;获得成功的

examples.en: I don't know how I can be a successful English learner.
examples.cn: 我不知道怎样才能成为一名成功的英语学习者。

examples.en: He was proud of having such a good friend.
examples.cn: 他为有这样的好朋友而自豪。

examples.en: Suddenly, all the lights went out and people had to wait in the darkness.
examples.cn: 突然,所有的灯都熄灭了,人们不得不在黑暗中等待。

expand: sudden adj. 突然的;忽然的

examples.en: I often suffer from unaccountable headaches.
examples.cn: 我常莫名其妙地头疼。

examples.en: Students observed the solution of sugar in tea.
examples.cn: 学生们观察了糖在茶中溶解的情况。

examples.en: I suggested teaching the foreign students how to use chopsticks.
examples.cn: 我建议教外国学生如何使用筷子。

examples.en: Shall I give you a written suggestion?
examples.cn: 需要我给您一份书面建议吗?

examples.en: David didn't know where he was going to spend his holiday this summer.
examples.cn: 今年夏天戴维不知道要去哪里度假。

examples.en: I want to sit in the sun.
examples.cn: 我想在太阳下面坐一坐。

expand: sunny adj. 阳光充足的;晴朗的

examples.en: There were many visitors in the Science Museum last Sunday.
examples.cn: 上星期日科学博物馆有许多游客。

examples.en: Because of the warm and sunny weather, oranges grow very well here.
examples.cn: 因为气候温暖、阳光充足,这儿的橘子长得很好。

examples.en: All the players in this game are super stars to the fans.
examples.cn: 对球迷而言,这场比赛中的所有球员都是超级巨星。

examples.en: How far is it from the school to the nearest supermarket?
examples.cn: 从学校到最近的超市有多远?

examples.en: Neither Betty nor Peter has potatoes for supper.
examples.cn: 无论是贝蒂还是彼得晚餐都没有吃土豆。

examples.en: He did a part-time job so that he could support his family.
examples.cn: 为了养家,他做了一份兼职工作。

examples.en: I suppose prices will go down.
examples.cn: 我想物价会下降。

translations.translation: 确信的,肯定的,有把握的

examples.en: Don't worry about the exam. You should be sure of yourselves.
examples.cn: 不要为考试担心。你们应该相信自己。

examples.en: About three-fourths of the earth's surface is covered by water.
examples.cn: 大约四分之三的地球表面被水覆盖。

translations.translation: 惊奇,诧异;意想不到(或突然)的事
使惊奇,使诧异,使感到意外

examples.en: I have a surprise for you.
examples.cn: 我要告诉你一件意想不到的事。

expand: surprised adj. 感到惊奇的,惊讶的,感觉意外的

translations.translation: 感到惊奇的,惊讶的,感觉意外的

examples.en: You will be surprised at how quickly the world around you will change.
examples.cn: 你会惊讶于周围的世界变化如此之快。

examples.en: The explorers climbed a mound to survey the land around them.
examples.cn: 探险者爬上一个土堆以测量他们四周的土地。

examples.en: It's important that these upland farms continue to survive.
examples.cn: 重要的是,这些高原农场能继续存在下去。

examples.en: You cannot sweep it up.
examples.cn: 你无法清除它。

examples.en: Her voice was as soft and sweet as a young girl's.
examples.cn: 她的声音和小女孩的一样温柔悦耳。

examples.en: Nobody taught me how to swim. I learnt it by myself.
examples.cn: 没有人教我如何游泳。我是自学的。

examples.en: The dove is a universal symbol of peace.
examples.cn: 鸽子被普遍认为是和平的象征。

examples.en: For the banking system, however, there are still signs of dislocation.
examples.cn: 不管怎样,就银行体系来说仍然存在混乱的迹象。

examples.en: This ticket belongs to my brother. Yours is on the table.
examples.cn: 这张票是我兄弟的。你的在桌子上。

translations.translation: 拿;拿走;做;吃;服用;乘坐(车、船);花费(时间);拍照

examples.en: The teacher agreed to let us take the test papers home.
examples.cn: 老师答应让我们把试卷带回家。

examples.en: The mother found that her son had a musical talent.
examples.cn: 母亲发现儿子有音乐天赋。

examples.en: President gave a talk on TV.
examples.cn: 总统在电视上作了一次演讲。

examples.en: Tommy is the tallest student in our class.
examples.cn: 汤米是我们班最高的学生。

examples.en: A dripping tap wastes water.
examples.cn: 滴水的龙头会浪费水。

examples.en: It's too noisy. I cannot hear the tape clearly.
examples.cn: 太吵了。我都听不清磁带了。

examples.en: The second task is to do something useful.
examples.cn: 第二项任务是做一件有意义的事情。

examples.en: The fruit from Hainan tastes nice. Will you taste some more?
examples.cn: 来自海南的水果味道不错。你要多尝一些吗?

expand: tasty adj. 美味的;可口的

examples.en: I don't often go to school by taxi.
examples.cn: 我不经常坐出租车去学校。

examples.en: Tea is the most popular drink in the world besides water.
examples.cn: 除了水,茶是世界上最流行的饮料。

translations.translation: 教书,教(某人);使(某人)明白或会做某事

examples.en: To make lessons lively, our teacher taught us English in a special way.
examples.cn: 为了使课堂气氛活跃,老师用一种特殊的方式教我们英语。

examples.en: Eric won't start the experiment until his teacher shows him how to do it.
examples.cn: 直到老师教他如何做实验,埃里克才开始动手。

examples.en: However, film-making is team work. You probably need many other people to help you.
examples.cn: 不管怎样,电影制作是团队工作。你可能需要许多人来帮助你。

examples.en: Her eyes filled with tears.
examples.cn: 她双眼噙满泪水。

examples.en: The technology in China is good.
examples.cn: 中国的技术很好。

examples.en: Board games are more and more popular among teenagers.
examples.cn: 棋类游戏在青少年中越来越流行了。

examples.en: I'll telephone you as soon as I get home.
examples.cn: 我一到家就给你打电话。

examples.en: The Smiths were watching TV when the telephone rang.
examples.cn: 史密斯一家正在看电视,这时电话响了。

examples.en: Who can tell me the meaning of that sign?
examples.cn: 谁能告诉我那个标志的含义?

examples.en: The food and medicine must be kept at a low temperature.
examples.cn: 食品和药物必须在低温下保存。

examples.en: Do you know where this temple is?
examples.cn: 你知道这座寺庙在哪里吗?

examples.en: I practise playing tennis every weekend.
examples.cn: 我每周末都练习打网球。

examples.en: George has made less progress in English this term than before.
examples.cn: 乔治这学期的英语进步比以前小。

examples.en: It is terrible to tell a lie.
examples.cn: 说谎是件很糟糕的事。

expand: terribly adv. 可怕地;非常,很

examples.en: Either measure the temperature with a thermometer or test the water with your wrist.
examples.cn: 要么用温度计测量水温,要么用你的手腕来试水温。

examples.en: The text is too difficult for me to understand.
examples.cn: 这篇课文对我来说太难理解了。

examples.en: He is more talented than she thinks.
examples.cn: 他比她想象的更有天赋。

examples.en: Thank you for offering us such a good meal.
examples.cn: 谢谢您为我们提供了这么可口的一餐。

expand: thankful adj. 感谢的,感激的

examples.en: The local people are thankful that the whole nation are helping them rebuild the town.
examples.cn: 当地群众感激全国人民帮助他们重建家园。

examples.en: That house is for sale.
examples.cn: 那套房子正在出售。

examples.en: During our visit to London we often went to the theatre.
examples.cn: 我们在伦敦逗留期间常去看戏。

translations.translation: 当时,那时;然后,后来;那么(通常用于句首或句尾)

examples.en: Then she began to cry.
examples.cn: 然后她就开始哭。

translations.translation: 在那里;往那里;(作引导词,与be动词连用,表示“存在,有”)

examples.en: I live near my school. It takes me only ten minutes to walk there.
examples.cn: 我住在学校附近。我步行到那里只需10分钟。

examples.en: Both he and I are very busy these days. We have decided not to go there.
examples.cn: 这些天我和他都很忙。我们已决定不去那儿了。

translations.translation: 厚的;浓的;浓密的;茂密的

examples.en: The blue book is thick.
examples.cn: 那本蓝色的书很厚。

examples.en: That boy is the thinnest one in his class.
examples.cn: 那个男孩是全班最瘦的。

examples.en: Water is a good thing.
examples.cn: 水是个好东西。

examples.en: We all think James will possibily be an artist when he grows up.
examples.cn: 我们都认为詹姆斯长大后可能成为一名艺术家。

examples.en: Would you pass me something to drink? I'm a bit thirsty.
examples.cn: 给我一些喝的,好吗?我有点口渴了。

examples.en: I like this coat better than that one.
examples.cn: 相比那件,我更喜欢这件大衣。

examples.en: Those children are lovely.
examples.cn: 那些孩子很可爱。

examples.en: Thought helps us solve problems.
examples.cn: 思考帮助我们解决问题。

examples.en: The thief was climbing through the window when the police arrived.
examples.cn: 警察到达时,小偷正从窗户爬出去。

examples.en: New scientific centres have been established throughout China.
examples.cn: 中国各地建立了许多新的科学研究中心。

examples.en: Don't throw rubbish everywhere!
examples.cn: 别乱丢垃圾!

examples.en: Thanksgiving Day is celebrated on the fourth Thursday in November in the U.S.A. every year.
examples.cn: 美国每年在11月的第4个星期四庆祝感恩节。

examples.en: Sarah doesn't know how she can book a plane ticket by telephone.
examples.cn: 萨拉不知道怎样通过电话预订机票。

examples.en: Edward, you have grown up. You should learn to make your own room tidy.
examples.cn: 爱德华,你已经长大了。你应该学会自己整理房间。

expand: untidy adj. 不整洁的,不干净的

translations.translation: (用绳、线)系,栓;(比赛或竞争中)得分相同

examples.en: Family ties can provide a sense of belonging and security in times of need.
examples.cn: 家庭纽带可以在需要时提供归属感和安全感。

examples.en: There are tigers in the forest.
examples.cn: 森林里有老虎。

examples.en: They had to wait till Monday to phone the bank.
examples.cn: 他们不得不等到星期一才打电话给银行。

translations.translation: 时间;时期;钟点;次,回;时代;年代

examples.en: It is time for lunch.
examples.cn: 吃中饭的时间到了。

phrase.cn: 玩得很愉快;过得很愉快

translations.translation: 尖端;实用的提示;小费;小窍门;建议;指点

examples.en: Do you have any small bills for the tip?
examples.cn: 你有没有给小费的小额钞票?

examples.en: They were all very tired, but none of them stopped to have a rest.
examples.cn: 他们都非常疲惫,但没有一个人停下来休息。

examples.en: The title of the article is Aliens.
examples.cn: 这篇文章的标题是《外星人》。

translations.translation: (表示接受动作的人或物)给...;对...,向...,到...

examples.en: It is time to go to school.
examples.cn: 到上学的时间了。

examples.en: The weather is pleasant today.
examples.cn: 今天天气令人愉快。

examples.en: What a nice day! Let's go for a picnic on the beach together.
examples.cn: 天气真不错啊!我们一起去沙滩上野餐吧。

examples.en: She spread some tomato paste on the fried fish.
examples.cn: 她在炸好的鱼上涂了一些番茄酱。

examples.en: Jane doesn't want to see the film War and Peace with her friend tomorrow.
examples.cn: 简明天不想和她的朋友一起去看电影《战争与和平》。

examples.en: Tom asked me if I was going to see the film tonight.
examples.cn: 汤姆问我今晚是否要去看电影。

examples.en: It's not safe for teenagers to give out too much information about themselves on the Internet.
examples.cn: 青少年在互联网上提供太多有关自己的信息,这是不安全的。

examples.en: The gardener's tools are kept in the shed.
examples.cn: 花匠的工具放在小屋里。

examples.en: It is necessary for everyone to brush his teeth after each meal.
examples.cn: 对每个人来说,餐后刷牙是必要的。

examples.en: If you don't clean your teeth regularly, you will get toothache.
examples.cn: 如果不定期清理牙齿,你会牙痛的。

examples.en: On the top of the building, tourists can enjoy a nice view of the city.
examples.cn: 在大楼的顶层,游客可以欣赏城市的美景。

examples.en: Let's change the topic!
examples.cn: 我们换个话题吧!

examples.en: Please don't touch anything.
examples.cn: 请不要碰任何东西。

translations.translation: 参观;观光;旅行;旅游;巡回演出

examples.en: Shall we take a tour to the Summer Palace, Mrs. White?
examples.cn: 怀特太太,我们去颐和园游览好吗?

expand: tourist n. 游客;旅客;旅行者

examples.en: Tourists enjoy swimming in the sea at the beautiful beaches in Bangkok.
examples.cn: 在曼谷美丽的海滩,游客享受着在海中游泳的乐趣。

expand: traditional adj. 传统的;习俗的

examples.cn: 一些西方人会在圣诞晚餐时享用传统的火鸡。

examples.cn: 我们应该遵守交通规则。

examples.cn: 学生昨天被要求把这篇文章翻译成英文。

examples.cn: 旅行使人心胸开阔。

examples.cn: 我们学校的学生多久种一次树?

examples.cn: 他对我耍了个伎俩,拒绝做他所许诺的事。

examples.cn: 在即将到来的二月,我们将有一次为期一周的家庭之旅去哈尔滨。

examples.cn: 我想知道怎样解决这个麻烦。

examples.cn: 恐怕这条裤子太小了。请您另外拿一条给我看看好吗?

examples.cn: 他开了好几年卡车,从没出过岔子。

examples.cn: 金鱼对渔夫说:“你所有的愿望都会成真。”

truth n. 真理;真相,实际情况;实情;事实

examples.en: There's a feeling of warmth and trust here.
examples.cn: 这里有一种温暖和信任的感觉。

translations.translation: 真理;真相,实际情况;实情;事实

examples.en: The police will try to find out the truth of the traffic accident.
examples.cn: 警方将试图查明这起交通事故的真相。

examples.en: Try to think how you will feel if you are hurt by others' unfriendly behaviours.
examples.cn: 如果你被别人不友好的行为伤害,试着想想你会有怎么样的感受。

examples.cn: 本周二是世界地球日。

examples.cn: 许多人在感恩节吃火鸡。

examples.en: Leaves turn yellow in autumn.
examples.cn: 秋天树叶变黄了。

phrase.cn: 关掉(电灯、电视、收音机等)
开,旋开(电灯、电视、收音机等)

examples.cn: 我们学校的报纸每月出版两次。

examples.en: He has a twin brother.
examples.cn: 他有一个孪生兄弟。

examples.en: I love this type of book.
examples.cn: 我喜欢这类书籍。

examples.cn: 你能为我打这封信吗?

examples.en: The weather in London is changeable, so you should take an umbrella with you.
examples.cn: 伦敦的天气多变,所以要随身带把伞。

examples.en: My uncle began to learn Chinese painting in his forties.
examples.cn: 我叔叔在40多岁时开始学画中国画。

examples.cn: 他下去之前,深深地吸了口气。

examples.cn: 我在地下停车场找到一个方便的停车位。

translations.translation: 在...下面划线;强调,使突出

examples.en: Read the passage and underline the topic of each paragraph.
examples.cn: 阅读这篇文章,划出每段的主题。

examples.en: Please pay attention to the underlined words.
examples.cn: 请注意划线部分的单词。

examples.cn: 我不明白老师在课堂上说什么,所以我举手了。

translations.translation: 不公正的;不公平的;违反规则或准则的

examples.cn: 让他承担一切费用似乎对他不公平。

examples.cn: 那次冲浪运动是我们两人都难以忘怀的经历。

examples.en: Unfortunately, my time is limited.
examples.cn: 可惜的是,我的时间有限。

translations.translation: 不开心的;不幸福的;难过的

examples.cn: 戴维在最近的英语考试中得了低分,这让他的父母不开心。

examples.cn: 当公众得知孩子们在学校吃了不健康的食物时,他们很愤怒。

examples.cn: 在我们学校,每个学生从星期一到星期五都必须穿校服。

examples.en: The family is a social unit.
examples.cn: 家庭是一个社会单位。

examples.en: They got united as one man.
examples.cn: 他们团结得就像一个人。

examples.en: My uncle is a university teacher. He is loved by all his students.
examples.cn: 我的叔叔是一名大学教师。学生们都爱他。

examples.en: I'll be able to finish the project on time unless there are unexpected delays.
examples.cn: 除非出现意外延误,否则我能按时完成这个项目。

examples.en: We shan't know the results of the test until tomorrow.
examples.cn: 我们明天才能知道考试结果。

examples.en: April Fool's Day is an unusual holiday. You can play a trick on anybody around you.
examples.cn: 愚人节是一个不寻常的节日。你可以捉弄身边任何人。

expand: usual adj. 通常的,平常的,寻常的

examples.en: He always gets up late.
examples.cn: 他总是很晚起床。

examples.en: What makes you so upset?
examples.cn: 是什么让你心烦意乱?

examples.en: You'll find it upstairs.
examples.cn: 你能在楼上找到。

examples.en: Her job is to show the customers how to use the computer.
examples.cn: 她的工作是教客户如何使用电脑。

expand: useful adj. 有用的;有益的
usefully adv. 有用地;有益地
useless adj. 无用的;废旧的

examples.cn: 对语言学习者提高写作能力来讲,这是一本非常有用的书。

examples.en: His advise is useless to our project.
examples.cn: 他的建议对我们的计划没有什么价值。

examples.cn: 他回家比平时晚。

examples.cn: 我通常乘地铁去学校。

examples.cn: 我们的价值体系与他们的并不相同。

translations.translation: 种种;种类;(同一事物的)不同种类,多种式样

examples.cn: 我们经营各种电子产品。

expand: various adj. 各种各样的;不同的

examples.cn: 由于种种原因,大家赴会都迟到了。

examples.en: I prefer vegetables to meat because they are good for my health.
examples.cn: 比起肉我更喜欢吃蔬菜,因为它们对我的身体健康有好处。

expand: vegetarian n. 素食者;吃素的人

examples.cn: 托尼的话让他的母亲感到非常兴奋。

examples.cn: 在比赛的最后一分钟,我们班戏剧性地战胜了一班。

examples.en: The video cameras are so nice. I really don't know which to choose.
examples.cn: 这些摄像机都这么好。我真的不知道该选哪个。

translations.translation: (个人的)看法,见解;风景,景色,(尤指)乡间美景;视野

examples.cn: 我赞成你有关花零用钱的看法。这是合理的。

examples.en: Water pollution is one of the most serious problems in that village.
examples.cn: 在那个村里,水污染是最严重的问题之一。

examples.en: Mary plays the violin very well.
examples.cn: 玛丽小提琴拉得很好。

examples.cn: 2月13日,我们开始了对美国的访问。

expand: visitor n. 参观者;访问者

examples.cn: 每天旅客入住前,我们都要仔细检查他们的护照。

examples.cn: 她说话声很柔和。

examples.cn: 志愿者们跟随运动员一起跑,以确保他们最终安全到达。

examples.cn: 我们都知道,让别人久等是不礼貌的。

expand: waitress n. 女侍者,女服务员

examples.cn: 玛丽的兄弟在一家五星级酒店当服务员。

examples.en: We asked the waitress for another glass of wine.
examples.cn: 我们请那位女侍者再来一杯酒。

examples.cn: 多娜醒来发现自己躺在医院的病床上。

expand: awake v. (使)醒来;唤起;激发起

examples.cn: 晚饭后,我们在家附近散步时,天开始下雨了。

examples.en: The wall was painted blue.
examples.cn: 墙壁被漆成蓝色。

examples.en: There isn't much bread here, but you can take a little if you want to.
examples.cn: 这里没有多少面包,但如果你想要你可以拿一点。

examples.en: The war made millions of people homeless.
examples.cn: 战争使数百万人无家可归。

examples.en: It is warm in spring.
examples.cn: 春天天气暖和。

examples.cn: 警察告诫孩子们不要在繁忙的马路边玩耍。

examples.cn: 妈妈把地毯洗了两次,现在是一尘不染。

examples.cn: 请快速冲个淋浴,不要浪费水。

examples.cn: 查利发现他有块和司机一样的手表。

examples.cn: 弗兰克在水下屏住呼吸,在游泳池里寻找他的戒指。

examples.en: He gave me a wave of the hand to say goodbye.
examples.cn: 他向我挥手告别。

examples.en: She spoke in a weak voice.
examples.cn: 她用微弱的声音说话。

examples.cn: 健康是真正的财富。

examples.cn: 他们可以看清黑板上的字,所以不需要戴眼镜。

examples.cn: 我不喜欢今年2月的天气,因为有很多雨天。

examples.cn: 数百家互联网服务商和网络公司在他们网站上对互联网协议第6版进行了测试。

examples.en: I couldn't get much news of the exhibition of clean-energy products from the website.
examples.cn: 我从网站上看不到很多关于清洁能源产品展览会的消息。

examples.cn: 会议已推迟到下星期三下午。

examples.en: Some questions were raised in their class meeting last week.
examples.cn: 在上星期的班会上有人提了一些问题。

examples.en: He goes to school on weekdays.
examples.cn: 他工作日去学校上学。

examples.en: We used to stay at the Browns' for the weekend.
examples.cn: 我们常常待在布朗家过周末。

examples.en: How much does that typewriter weigh?
examples.cn: 那台打字机有多重?

examples.en: How can Lisa lose weight so successfully in such a short time?
examples.cn: 莉萨如何能在这么短的时间内减肥成功?

examples.cn: 他在剑桥受到了热烈的欢迎。

examples.en: I don't feel well today.
examples.cn: 我今天感到不舒服。

examples.en: The wind was blowing lightly from the west.
examples.cn: 风从西面轻轻吹来。

expand: western adj. 西方的;西部的

examples.en: Which kind of food do you prefer, Chinese or Western?
examples.cn: 你喜欢吃中餐,还是喜欢吃西餐?

examples.en: It is wet in the South, while the North is dry.
examples.cn: 南方雨水充沛,北方则比较干燥。

translations.translation: (表示疑问)什么;(表示建议)怎么样

examples.cn: 你叫什么名字?

examples.en: What about going for a walk?
examples.cn: 去散散步怎么样?

examples.cn: 当你遇到麻烦时,好朋友总会向你伸出援助之手。

examples.en: Joyce has a good memory. She still remembers where she lived in her childhood.
examples.cn: 乔伊丝记忆力很好。她还记得童年生活过的地方。

examples.en: I don't know whether you like flowers, sir.
examples.cn: 我不知道您是否喜欢花,先生。

examples.en: Which T-shirt do you like better, the red one or the blue one?
examples.cn: 你更喜欢哪件T恤衫,红色的还是蓝色的?

examples.cn: 昨晚当我母亲在洗衣服时,我父亲在为他的演讲做准备。

examples.cn: 华盛顿另一个世界著名的建筑物是白宫。

examples.en: Who do you think will win the first prize?
examples.cn: 你觉得谁会赢得第一名呢?

examples.cn: 袁隆平虽然离开了我们,但他在“杂交水稻”方面的杰出贡献将对整个世界产生巨大影响。

examples.en: Did you know whom Bill was waiting for?
examples.cn: 你知道比尔在等谁吗?

examples.en: Whose books are these?
examples.cn: 这些书是谁的?

examples.en: Nobody knows why Betty has become so forgetful in recent years.
examples.cn: 没有人知道为什么近年来贝蒂变得如此健忘。

examples.en: They came to a wide river.
examples.cn: 他们来到了一条宽阔的河边。

expand: widely adv. 宽阔地;广泛地;普遍地

examples.cn: 随着中国的发展,汉语已成为一种国际语言,在世界各地被广泛使用。

examples.en: The town government has decided to widen this main street.
examples.cn: 市政府决定拓宽这条主街。

examples.en: Mr. Smith and his wife seldom drive their car to work, do they?
examples.cn: 史密斯先生和他的妻子很少开车上班,是吗?

translations.translation: 自然生长的,野的,野生的;荒凉的

examples.en: We should protect the wild animal.
examples.cn: 我们应该保护野生动物。

translations.translation: (表示将来)将;会;愿意;(表示提问)是否愿意;...好吗?

examples.en: Our headmaster will make a speech to the parents on the School Open Day.
examples.cn: 在学校开放日,我们的校长将向家长发表讲话。

examples.en: Nobody knows which player will win the game until the last moment.
examples.cn: 不到最后一刻没人知道哪位运动员会赢得这场比赛。

expand: winner n. 获胜者;优胜者

examples.en: Wind is a motive power.
examples.cn: 风是一种动力。

expand: windy adj. 有风的;起风的

examples.en: Could you possibly open that window for me?
examples.cn: 你能为我打开那扇窗吗?

examples.en: What fun it is to surf on a windy day!
examples.cn: 在有风的日子冲浪是多么有趣啊!

examples.en: You won't be able to make the best wine unless you choose the perfect grapes only.
examples.cn: 只有选用极好的葡萄,才能酿造出最好的酒。

examples.en: Friendship is love without wing.
examples.cn: 友谊是无翼之爱。

examples.cn: 吴良镛是国家最高科学技术奖的获奖者之一。

examples.cn: 林小姐问迪克今年冬天他是否要去游览长城。

examples.cn: 智慧比财富更珍贵。

expand: wise adj. 聪明的;明智的

translations.translation: 聪明的;明智的;充满智慧的

examples.en: They made a wise decision to leave there in a hurry before the heavy rain.
examples.cn: 他们做了一个明智的决定,大雨前匆忙离开了那里。

examples.cn: 我的愿望是长大后成为一名科学家。贝蒂,你的愿望是什么?

translations.translation: 与...一道;跟...一起;带有;具有;关于;以;和;用;有

examples.cn: 那位著名演员经常和他的孩子们在公园玩。

examples.en: The house is within eyesight.
examples.cn: 这幢房子在视线范围之内。

examples.en: Without the glasses, he can't see the words on the blackboard clearly.
examples.cn: 没戴眼镜,他看不清黑板上的字。

examples.en: They want to kill the wolf.
examples.cn: 他们想要把狼打死。

examples.en: These women doctors have saved many children's lives since they worked in the hospital.
examples.cn: 自从这些女医生在医院工作,她们救了很多孩子的生命。

examples.cn: 我想知道中国的大学校园什么时候将对公众开放。

wonderfully adv. 非常;令人惊奇地

examples.cn: 在他的生日聚会上,我们度过了如此美好的时光。

examples.en: Paper is made from wood.
examples.cn: 纸是由木头制成的。

examples.cn: 史密斯先生最近在花园里的池塘上建造了一座木桥。

examples.cn: 我无法理解这句句子的意思,尽管句中没有新单词。

examples.cn: 直到所有的工人都得救了,消防队员才停止工作。

examples.en: The workers were asked to go back to work at once.
examples.cn: 工人们被要求立刻回去工作。

examples.cn: 每年上海吸引很多来自世界各地的游客。

examples.cn: 你已经尽力了,所以不必太担心这次考试。

examples.cn: 不值得花这么多时间在园艺上。

translations.translation: 愿意;(客气地建议或邀请)将;将会

examples.en: She said she would come.
examples.cn: 她说过她会来的。

phrase.cn: 想要;(表示喜欢、愿意)很想;很愿意

examples.en: My wound is still painful.
examples.cn: 我的伤口还在痛。

examples.en: This is the wounded soldier.
examples.cn: 这就是那位受伤的战士。

examples.en: He wrote his first symphony when he was 16.
examples.cn: 他16岁时写了自己的第一部交响曲。

examples.en: Who is the writer of the book War and Peace?
examples.cn: 《战争与和平》这部书的作者是谁?

translations.translation: 错误的;不正常的;有病的

examples.en: It's wrong of you to make fun of the disabled boy. You should apologize to him.
examples.cn: 你取笑那个残疾男孩是不对的。你应该向他道歉。

examples.en: What changeable weather it is this year!
examples.cn: 今年的天气真是多变啊!

examples.en: Yellow is my favourite colour.
examples.cn: 黄色是我最喜欢的颜色。

examples.en: In yesterday's games, Switzerland beat the United States two to one.
examples.cn: 在昨天的比赛中,瑞士队2比1打败了美国队。

examples.en: Has Danny given up smoking yet?
examples.cn: 丹尼戒烟了吗?

examples.en: Do you have any low-fat yogurt?
examples.cn: 你有没有低脂的酸奶?

examples.en: She must be at least forty, but she likes dressing up as a young girl.
examples.cn: 她至少有40岁了,但她喜欢打扮成年轻的姑娘。

examples.en: It's a sunny late winter day, just a few degrees above zero.
examples.cn: 这是晚冬晴朗的一天,只有零上几度。

examples.en: Please take me to the zoo.
examples.cn: 请带我去动物园。
